              Our field teams identify the most vulnerable children through community assessments. Priority is given to children who have lost their father or both parents and whose families cannot meet their basic needs. Each child is carefully evaluated to ensure they receive the support they need most.
            </div>
          </details>
          <details class="border-b border-gray-200 group">
            <summary class="flex items-center gap-4 py-5 cursor-pointer list-none hover:bg-gray-50/50 transition">
              <span class="text-2xl text-gray-400 group-open:text-[#1a6fb5] font-light leading-none transition select-none">+</span>
              <span class="font-semibold text-gray-800" style="font-family: 'Signika', sans-serif;">Why should I sponsor with Qurbani Foundation?</span>
            </summary>
            <div class="pl-10 pb-5 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
              Qurbani Foundation maintains a 100% donation policy — every dollar of your sponsorship goes directly to your orphan's care. We provide true 1-to-1 sponsorship, annual progress reports, and transparent reporting. As a registered 501(c)(3) nonprofit, all donations are tax-deductible.
            </div>
          </details>
          <details class="border-b border-gray-200 group">
            <summary class="flex items-center gap-4 py-5 cursor-pointer list-none hover:bg-gray-50/50 transition">
              <span class="text-2xl text-gray-400 group-open:text-[#1a6fb5] font-light leading-none transition select-none">+</span>
              <span class="font-semibold text-gray-800" style="font-family: 'Signika', sans-serif;">Is orphan sponsorship Zakat eligible?</span>
            </summary>
            <div class="pl-10 pb-5 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
              Yes! 100% of orphan sponsorship donations are Zakat eligible. We ensure your Zakat reaches children who meet all Islamic criteria for Zakat recipients.
            </div>
          </details>
        </div>

        <!-- Category 2: Financial and Payment Inquiries -->
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#1a6fb5] mb-6" style="font-family: 'Signika', sans-serif;">Financial and Payment Inquiries</h3>
        <div class="space-y-0 mb-12">
          <details class="border-b border-gray-200 group">
            <summary class="flex items-center gap-4 py-5 cursor-pointer list-none hover:bg-gray-50/50 transition">
              <span class="text-2xl text-gray-400 group-open:text-[#1a6fb5] font-light leading-none transition select-none">+</span>
              <span class="font-semibold text-gray-800" style="font-family: 'Signika', sans-serif;">How much of my sponsorship money will reach the orphan?</span>
            </summary>
            <div class="pl-10 pb-5 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
              100% of your sponsorship goes directly to child care — education, food, healthcare, and shelter. Administrative costs are covered separately through institutional grants and are never taken from your charitable contributions.
            </div>
          </details>
          <details class="border-b border-gray-200 group">
            <summary class="flex items-center gap-4 py-5 cursor-pointer list-none hover:bg-gray-50/50 transition">
              <span class="text-2xl text-gray-400 group-open:text-[#1a6fb5] font-light leading-none transition select-none">+</span>
              <span class="font-semibold text-gray-800" style="font-family: 'Signika', sans-serif;">Does the orphan receive sponsorship money every month?</span>
            </summary>
            <div class="pl-10 pb-5 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
              Your monthly gift is sent to our field offices on a quarterly basis for immediate distribution to your sponsored orphan. This ensures efficient fund transfers while maintaining consistent support for the child throughout the year.
            </div>
          </details>
          <details class="border-b border-gray-200 group">
            <summary class="flex items-center gap-4 py-5 cursor-pointer list-none hover:bg-gray-50/50 transition">
              <span class="text-2xl text-gray-400 group-open:text-[#1a6fb5] font-light leading-none transition select-none">+</span>
              <span class="font-semibold text-gray-800" style="font-family: 'Signika', sans-serif;">How long will the sponsorship continue?</span>
            </summary>
            <div class="pl-10 pb-5 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
              Sponsorship continues until the child reaches adulthood (18 years) or becomes self-sufficient. Many sponsors maintain relationships with their children even after they graduate from the program.
            </div>
          </details>
          <details class="border-b border-gray-200 group">
            <summary class="flex items-center gap-4 py-5 cursor-pointer list-none hover:bg-gray-50/50 transition">
              <span class="text-2xl text-gray-400 group-open:text-[#1a6fb5] font-light leading-none transition select-none">+</span>
              <span class="font-semibold text-gray-800" style="font-family: 'Signika', sans-serif;">Will my sponsorship always cost the same amount?</span>
            </summary>
            <div class="pl-10 pb-5 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
              We strive to keep sponsorship costs stable. In rare cases, costs may adjust due to inflation or changing needs in the field. If any change occurs, you will be notified well in advance and can adjust your commitment accordingly.
            </div>
          </details>
          <details class="border-b border-gray-200 group">
            <summary class="flex items-center gap-4 py-5 cursor-pointer list-none hover:bg-gray-50/50 transition">
              <span class="text-2xl text-gray-400 group-open:text-[#1a6fb5] font-light leading-none transition select-none">+</span>
              <span class="font-semibold text-gray-800" style="font-family: 'Signika', sans-serif;">What happens if I wish to cancel my sponsorship?</span>
            </summary>
            <div class="pl-10 pb-5 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
              We understand circumstances change. You can cancel anytime with no penalties. Your sponsored child will continue to receive care from our general fund while we find them a new sponsor.
            </div>
          </details>
          <details class="border-b border-gray-200 group">
            <summary class="flex items-center gap-4 py-5 cursor-pointer list-none hover:bg-gray-50/50 transition">
              <span class="text-2xl text-gray-400 group-open:text-[#1a6fb5] font-light leading-none transition select-none">+</span>
              <span class="font-semibold text-gray-800" style="font-family: 'Signika', sans-serif;">Will I always be sponsoring the same child?</span>
            </summary>
            <div class="pl-10 pb-5 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
              Yes, you will sponsor the same child for the duration of the program. In rare circumstances — such as a family relocating or a child aging out — we will notify you and match you with another child in need.
            </div>
          </details>
        </div>

        <!-- Category 3: Connecting with Your Sponsored Orphan -->
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#1a6fb5] mb-6" style="font-family: 'Signika', sans-serif;">Connecting with Your Sponsored Orphan</h3>
        <div class="space-y-0 mb-12">
          <details class="border-b border-gray-200 group">
            <summary class="flex items-center gap-4 py-5 cursor-pointer list-none hover:bg-gray-50/50 transition">
              <span class="text-2xl text-gray-400 group-open:text-[#1a6fb5] font-light leading-none transition select-none">+</span>
              <span class="font-semibold text-gray-800" style="font-family: 'Signika', sans-serif;">What information will I receive about the orphan I sponsor?</span>
            </summary>
            <div class="pl-10 pb-5 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
              Within 4-6 weeks of your first payment, you'll receive your child's biodata report including their name, age, city, and background story. For the safety and privacy of our children, we do not share photographs. You'll then receive annual progress reports with updates on their education, health, and overall wellbeing.
            </div>
          </details>
          <details class="border-b border-gray-200 group">
            <summary class="flex items-center gap-4 py-5 cursor-pointer list-none hover:bg-gray-50/50 transition">
              <span class="text-2xl text-gray-400 group-open:text-[#1a6fb5] font-light leading-none transition select-none">+</span>
              <span class="font-semibold text-gray-800" style="font-family: 'Signika', sans-serif;">Can I write a letter to my sponsored orphan?</span>
            </summary>
            <div class="pl-10 pb-5 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
              Yes! We facilitate letter exchange between sponsors and children. You can send letters and cards through our office, and our field team will deliver them. It's a beautiful way to build a personal connection with the child you're supporting.
            </div>
          </details>
          <details class="border-b border-gray-200 group">
            <summary class="flex items-center gap-4 py-5 cursor-pointer list-none hover:bg-gray-50/50 transition">
              <span class="text-2xl text-gray-400 group-open:text-[#1a6fb5] font-light leading-none transition select-none">+</span>
              <span class="font-semibold text-gray-800" style="font-family: 'Signika', sans-serif;">Can I meet with my sponsored orphan?</span>
            </summary>
            <div class="pl-10 pb-5 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
              In some cases, field visits can be arranged through our local offices, subject to security and logistical considerations. Contact our donor care team at info@qurbani.com to inquire about visiting your sponsored child.
            </div>
          </details>
          <details class="border-b border-gray-200 group">
            <summary class="flex items-center gap-4 py-5 cursor-pointer list-none hover:bg-gray-50/50 transition">
              <span class="text-2xl text-gray-400 group-open:text-[#1a6fb5] font-light leading-none transition select-none">+</span>
              <span class="font-semibold text-gray-800" style="font-family: 'Signika', sans-serif;">Can I send a gift to my orphan?</span>
            </summary>
            <div class="pl-10 pb-5 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
              Yes! You can send small gifts during Eid and special occasions. Our field team ensures safe and appropriate delivery. Contact us for guidelines on what can be sent to each country.
            </div>
          </details>
        </div>

        <!-- Privacy Notice -->
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-xs leading-relaxed italic">
          Qurbani Foundation is committed to protecting the privacy and confidentiality of all individuals involved in the sponsorship program including children, their families and guardians, and donors. Any personal data collected for administering the sponsorship program will be strictly processed in accordance with our Privacy Policy and relevant data protection legislation.
        </p>

        <!-- Still Have Questions -->
        <div class="mt-12 bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 text-center shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2" style="font-family: 'Signika', sans-serif;">Still have questions?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Our donor care team is here to help</p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-4">
            <a href="tel:18009000027" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-[#1a6fb5] font-semibold hover:underline">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z"/>
              </svg>
              1-800-900-0027
            </a>
            <span class="text-gray-300">|</span>
            <a href="mailto:info@qurbani.com" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-[#1a6fb5] font-semibold hover:underline">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"/>
              </svg>
              info@qurbani.com
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <!-- Sticky Mobile CTA -->
  <div class="fixed bottom-0 left-0 right-0 bg-white border-t border-gray-200 p-4 lg:hidden z-50 shadow-lg">
    <button
      id="mobile-sponsor-btn"
      class="w-full bg-[#d97706] text-white font-bold text-lg py-4 px-6 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center gap-2 shadow-lg active:scale-[0.98] transition-transform"
      style="font-family: 'Signika', sans-serif;"
    >
      <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
        <path d="M12 21.35l-1.45-1.32C5.4 15.36 2 12.28 2 8.5 2 5.42 4.42 3 7.5 3c1.74 0 3.41.81 4.5 2.09C13.09 3.81 14.76 3 16.5 3 19.58 3 22 5.42 22 8.5c0 3.78-3.4 6.86-8.55 11.54L12 21.35z"/>
      </svg>
      <span id="mobile-btn-text">Sponsor an Orphan</span>
      <svg id="mobile-btn-arrow" class="w-5 h-5 ml-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/>
      </svg>
    </button>
  </div>

  <Footer />
</Layout>

<script is:inline define:vars={{ campaignId: campaign.id, campaignTitle: campaign.title, campaignSlug: campaign.slug, effectiveBasePrice }}>
  // Track view_item in GA4 on page load
  if (window.trackViewItem) {
    window.trackViewItem({
      id: campaignId,
      name: campaignTitle,
      slug: campaignSlug,
      amount: 45, // Base sponsorship amount
      campaign: 'orphan-sponsorship'
    });
  }
  // Make effectiveBasePrice available to the next script
  window.__effectiveBasePrice = effectiveBasePrice;
</script>

<script is:inline>
  document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
    // Elements
    const countryBtns = document.querySelectorAll('.country-btn');
    const qtyTiles = document.querySelectorAll('.qty-tile');
    const customToggle = document.getElementById('custom-toggle');
    const customQtyInput = document.getElementById('custom-qty-input');
    const customQty = document.getElementById('custom-qty');
    const customDecrease = document.getElementById('custom-decrease');
    const customIncrease = document.getElementById('custom-increase');
    const customTotal = document.getElementById('custom-total');
    // Mobile custom qty elements (class-based since they duplicate the desktop ones)
    const mobileCustomQty = document.querySelector('.custom-qty-field');
    const mobileCustomDecrease = document.querySelector('.custom-decrease-btn');
    const mobileCustomIncrease = document.querySelector('.custom-increase-btn');
    const mobileCustomTotal = document.querySelector('.custom-total-display');
    const freqMonthly = document.getElementById('freq-monthly');
    const freqYearly = document.getElementById('freq-yearly');
    const sponsorBtn = document.getElementById('sponsor-btn');
    const mobileSponsorBtn = document.getElementById('mobile-sponsor-btn');

    // Summary elements
    const summaryQty = document.getElementById('summary-qty');
    const summaryCountry = document.getElementById('summary-country');
    const summaryAmount = document.getElementById('summary-amount');
    const amountLabel = document.getElementById('amount-label');
    const summaryDaily = document.getElementById('summary-daily');
    const visualStack = document.getElementById('visual-stack');
    const btnText = document.getElementById('btn-text');
    const mobileBtnText = document.getElementById('mobile-btn-text');

    // Show More Countries toggle (both mobile and desktop)
    let countriesExpanded = false;
    const toggleMoreCountries = (btn) => {
      countriesExpanded = !countriesExpanded;
      // Toggle desktop
      const desktopMore = document.getElementById('more-countries');
      if (desktopMore) {
        if (countriesExpanded) {
          desktopMore.classList.remove('hidden');
          desktopMore.classList.add('grid');
        } else {
          desktopMore.classList.add('hidden');
          desktopMore.classList.remove('grid');
        }
      }
      // Toggle mobile
      const mobileMore = document.getElementById('more-countries-mobile');
      if (mobileMore) mobileMore.classList.toggle('hidden', !countriesExpanded);
      // Update all button texts/icons
      document.querySelectorAll('.more-text').forEach(t => t.textContent = countriesExpanded ? 'Show less' : 'More countries');
      document.querySelectorAll('.more-icon').forEach(i => i.style.transform = countriesExpanded ? 'rotate(180deg)' : 'rotate(0deg)');
    };
    document.getElementById('show-more-countries')?.addEventListener('click', function() { toggleMoreCountries(this); });
    document.querySelector('.show-more-countries-btn')?.addEventListener('click', function() { toggleMoreCountries(this); });

    // Show More Quantities toggle (mobile)
    let qtyExpanded = false;
    const showMoreQtyBtn = document.querySelector('.show-more-qty-btn');
    showMoreQtyBtn?.addEventListener('click', () => {
      qtyExpanded = !qtyExpanded;
      const moreQty = document.getElementById('more-quantities-mobile');
      if (moreQty) moreQty.classList.toggle('hidden', !qtyExpanded);
      const txt = document.querySelector('.more-qty-text');
      if (txt) txt.textContent = qtyExpanded ? 'Show less' : 'More options';
      const icon = document.querySelector('.more-qty-icon');
      if (icon) icon.style.transform = qtyExpanded ? 'rotate(180deg)' : 'rotate(0deg)';
    });

    // Hero CTA button - scroll to region on click
    const heroCta = document.getElementById('hero-cta-btn');
    heroCta?.addEventListener('click', () => {
      const region = document.getElementById('region-section');
      if (region) {
        const offset = 100;
        const pos = region.getBoundingClientRect().top + window.pageYOffset;
        window.scrollTo({ top: pos - offset, behavior: 'smooth' });
      }
    });

    // State
    let selectedCountry = null;
    let selectedQty = 0;
    let basePrice = window.__effectiveBasePrice || 45;
    let isMonthly = true;
    let isCustom = false;
    const summaryQtyLabel = document.getElementById('summary-qty-label');

    // Check if both selections are made
    const isSelectionComplete = () => {
      return selectedCountry !== null && selectedQty > 0;
    };

    // Section elements for scrolling
    const regionSection = document.getElementById('region-section');
    const quantitySection = document.getElementById('quantity-section');
    const step1Badge = document.getElementById('step-1-badge');
    const step2Badge = document.getElementById('step-2-badge');
    const mobileArrow = document.getElementById('mobile-btn-arrow');

    // Scroll to element with offset for mobile sticky bar
    const scrollToSection = (element, highlight = true) => {
      if (!element) return;

      const offset = 100; // Account for header
      const elementPosition = element.getBoundingClientRect().top + window.pageYOffset;

      window.scrollTo({
        top: elementPosition - offset,
        behavior: 'smooth'
      });

      if (highlight) {
        // Add subtle highlight
        element.classList.add('outline', 'outline-2', 'outline-[#d97706]/60');
        setTimeout(() => {
          element.classList.remove('outline', 'outline-2', 'outline-[#d97706]/60');
        }, 1500);
      }
    };

    // Show a brief toast message when country isn't selected
    const showSelectCountryToast = () => {
      // Remove any existing toast
      document.getElementById('country-toast')?.remove();
      const toast = document.createElement('div');
      toast.id = 'country-toast';
      toast.className = 'fixed top-20 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 z-50 bg-[#d97706] text-white px-5 py-3 rounded-xl shadow-lg flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-medium transition-all duration-300';
      toast.innerHTML = `
        <svg class="w-5 h-5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M7 11l5-5m0 0l5 5m-5-5v12"/>
        </svg>
        Please select a country first
      `;
      document.body.appendChild(toast);
      // Auto-dismiss after 2.5s
      setTimeout(() => {
        toast.style.opacity = '0';
        toast.style.transform = 'translate(-50%, -10px)';
        setTimeout(() => toast.remove(), 300);
      }, 2500);
    };

    // Attach click listener to visual stack link
    const attachVisualStackListener = () => {
      const link = document.querySelector('.visual-stack-link');
      if (link) {
        link.addEventListener('click', () => {
          if (!selectedCountry) {
            scrollToSection(regionSection, true);
          } else if (selectedQty === 0) {
            scrollToSection(quantitySection, true);
          }
        });
      }
    };

    // Update button state and appearance
    const updateButtonState = () => {
      const complete = isSelectionComplete();

      // Remove continuous highlight classes first (re-applied below if needed)
      sponsorBtn?.classList.remove('animate-highlight-continuous');
      mobileSponsorBtn?.classList.remove('animate-highlight-continuous');

      if (complete) {
        // Enable desktop button
        sponsorBtn?.removeAttribute('disabled');
        sponsorBtn?.classList.remove('bg-gray-300', 'text-gray-500', 'cursor-not-allowed');
        sponsorBtn?.classList.add('bg-[#d97706]', 'hover:bg-[#b45309]', 'text-white', 'shadow-lg', 'hover:shadow-xl', 'transform', 'hover:-translate-y-0.5');

        // Mobile button shows ready state - hide arrow
        if (mobileArrow) mobileArrow.classList.add('hidden');
      } else if (selectedQty > 0 && !selectedCountry) {
        // Children selected but no country — make button orange + continuous pulse to draw attention
        sponsorBtn?.removeAttribute('disabled');
        sponsorBtn?.classList.remove('bg-gray-300', 'text-gray-500', 'cursor-not-allowed');
        sponsorBtn?.classList.add('bg-[#d97706]', 'hover:bg-[#b45309]', 'text-white', 'shadow-lg', 'hover:shadow-xl', 'transform', 'hover:-translate-y-0.5');
        sponsorBtn?.classList.add('animate-highlight-continuous');
        mobileSponsorBtn?.classList.add('animate-highlight-continuous');

        // Mobile arrow pointing up to indicate "go select country"
        if (mobileArrow) mobileArrow.classList.remove('hidden');
      } else {
        // Nothing selected or only country selected
        sponsorBtn?.setAttribute('disabled', 'true');
        sponsorBtn?.classList.add('bg-gray-300', 'text-gray-500', 'cursor-not-allowed');
        sponsorBtn?.classList.remove('bg-[#d97706]', 'hover:bg-[#b45309]', 'text-white', 'shadow-lg', 'hover:shadow-xl', 'transform', 'hover:-translate-y-0.5');

        // Mobile button shows arrow to indicate scrolling action
        if (mobileArrow) mobileArrow.classList.remove('hidden');
      }

      // Update step badges to show completion
      if (selectedCountry && step1Badge) {
        step1Badge.innerHTML = '<svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>';
        step1Badge.classList.add('bg-green-500');
        step1Badge.classList.remove('bg-[#d97706]');
      }
      if (selectedQty > 0 && step2Badge) {
        step2Badge.innerHTML = '<svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>';
        step2Badge.classList.add('bg-green-500');
        step2Badge.classList.remove('bg-[#d97706]');
      }
    };

    // Update UI
    const updateUI = () => {
      // Update tile prices based on selected country multiplier
      const mult = selectedCountry?.multiplier || 1;
      qtyTiles.forEach(tile => {
        const qty = parseInt(tile.dataset.qty || '1');
        const newMonthly = Math.round(qty * basePrice * mult);
        tile.dataset.monthly = newMonthly.toString();
        // Find the price element inside .text-center
        const textCenter = tile.querySelector('.text-center');
        if (textCenter) {
          const priceDiv = textCenter.querySelectorAll('div')[1];
          if (priceDiv) {
            priceDiv.innerHTML = '$' + newMonthly + '<span class="text-xs text-gray-400">/mo</span>';
          }
        }
      });

      // If nothing selected yet, show placeholder state
      if (!selectedCountry && selectedQty === 0) {
        if (summaryQty) summaryQty.textContent = '-';
        if (summaryQtyLabel) {
          summaryQtyLabel.textContent = 'Select a region to start';
          summaryQtyLabel.classList.add('text-[#d97706]', 'font-medium', 'hover:underline', 'cursor-pointer');
          summaryQtyLabel.classList.remove('text-gray-600');
        }
        if (summaryCountry) summaryCountry.textContent = 'Select a region';
        if (summaryAmount) summaryAmount.textContent = '$0';
        if (summaryDaily) summaryDaily.textContent = '$0.00/day';
        if (visualStack) {
          visualStack.innerHTML = `
            <svg class="w-10 h-14 text-gray-300" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <circle cx="12" cy="4" r="3"/>
              <path d="M12 8c-3.5 0-6 2.5-6 6v6h3v-4h6v4h3v-6c0-3.5-2.5-6-6-6z"/>
            </svg>
          `;
        }
        if (btnText) btnText.textContent = 'Sponsor an Orphan';
        if (mobileBtnText) mobileBtnText.textContent = 'Sponsor an Orphan';
        // Hide mobile price summary
        const mps = document.getElementById('mobile-price-summary');
        if (mps) mps.classList.add('hidden');
        updateButtonState();
        return;
      }

      const multiplier = selectedCountry?.multiplier || 1;
      const monthlyTotal = selectedQty * basePrice * multiplier;
      const yearlyTotal = monthlyTotal * 12;
      const daily = monthlyTotal / 30;

      // Summary
      if (summaryQty) {
        if (selectedQty > 0) {
          summaryQty.textContent = selectedQty.toString();
          if (summaryQtyLabel) {
            summaryQtyLabel.textContent = selectedQty === 1 ? 'child will receive care' : 'children will receive care';
            summaryQtyLabel.classList.remove('text-[#d97706]', 'font-medium', 'hover:underline', 'cursor-pointer');
            summaryQtyLabel.classList.add('text-gray-600');
          }
        } else {
          summaryQty.textContent = '-';
          if (summaryQtyLabel) {
            summaryQtyLabel.classList.add('text-[#d97706]', 'font-medium', 'hover:underline', 'cursor-pointer');
            summaryQtyLabel.classList.remove('text-gray-600');
            if (selectedCountry) {
              summaryQtyLabel.textContent = 'Now select children';
            } else {
              summaryQtyLabel.textContent = 'Select a region to start';
            }
          }
        }
      }

      if (summaryCountry) {
        if (selectedCountry) {
          summaryCountry.textContent = `${selectedCountry.flag} ${selectedCountry.name}`;
          summaryCountry.classList.remove('text-[#d97706]', 'hover:underline', 'cursor-pointer');
          summaryCountry.classList.add('text-gray-800');
        } else {
          summaryCountry.textContent = 'Select a region';
          summaryCountry.classList.add('text-[#d97706]', 'hover:underline', 'cursor-pointer');
          summaryCountry.classList.remove('text-gray-800');
        }
      }

      // Update amounts based on frequency selection
      if (selectedQty > 0) {
        if (isMonthly) {
          if (amountLabel) amountLabel.textContent = 'Monthly';
          if (summaryAmount) summaryAmount.textContent = `$${monthlyTotal.toFixed(0)}`;
          if (summaryDaily) summaryDaily.textContent = `$${daily.toFixed(2)}/day`;
        } else {
          if (amountLabel) amountLabel.textContent = 'Yearly';
          if (summaryAmount) summaryAmount.textContent = `$${yearlyTotal.toLocaleString()}`;
          if (summaryDaily) summaryDaily.textContent = `$${(yearlyTotal / 365).toFixed(2)}/day`;
        }
      } else {
        if (summaryAmount) summaryAmount.textContent = '$0';
        if (summaryDaily) summaryDaily.textContent = '$0.00/day';
      }

      // Button text - action-oriented
      if (isSelectionComplete()) {
        const childText = selectedQty === 1 ? 'Child' : 'Children';
        const buttonLabel = `Sponsor ${selectedQty} ${childText}`;
        if (btnText) btnText.textContent = buttonLabel;
        if (mobileBtnText) mobileBtnText.textContent = buttonLabel;
      } else {
        // Not complete yet - keep the primary CTA
        if (btnText) btnText.textContent = 'Sponsor an Orphan';
        if (mobileBtnText) mobileBtnText.textContent = 'Sponsor an Orphan';
      }

      // Visual stack - shows child icons when quantity is selected
      if (visualStack) {
        if (selectedQty > 0) {
          const count = Math.min(selectedQty, 6);
          let html = '';
          for (let i = 0; i < count; i++) {
            const opacity = 1 - i * 0.12;
            html += `<svg class="w-10 h-14 text-gray-700" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" style="opacity: ${opacity};">
              <circle cx="12" cy="4" r="3"/>
              <path d="M12 8c-3.5 0-6 2.5-6 6v6h3v-4h6v4h3v-6c0-3.5-2.5-6-6-6z"/>
            </svg>`;
          }
          if (selectedQty > 6) {
            html += `<span class="ml-2 text-lg font-bold text-gray-700">+${selectedQty - 6}</span>`;
          }
          visualStack.innerHTML = html;
        } else {
          // Empty state - just show placeholder icons in gray
          visualStack.innerHTML = `
            <svg class="w-10 h-14 text-gray-300" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <circle cx="12" cy="4" r="3"/>
              <path d="M12 8c-3.5 0-6 2.5-6 6v6h3v-4h6v4h3v-6c0-3.5-2.5-6-6-6z"/>
            </svg>
          `;
        }
      }

      // Custom total
      if (isCustom) {
        const totalText = `$${monthlyTotal.toFixed(0)}`;
        if (customTotal) customTotal.textContent = totalText;
        if (mobileCustomTotal) mobileCustomTotal.textContent = totalText;
      }

      // Mobile price summary
      const mobilePriceSummary = document.getElementById('mobile-price-summary');
      const mobileTotalPrice = document.getElementById('mobile-total-price');
      const mobilePriceDetail = document.getElementById('mobile-price-detail');
      const mobileDailyPrice = document.getElementById('mobile-daily-price');

      if (mobilePriceSummary && selectedQty > 0 && selectedCountry) {
        mobilePriceSummary.classList.remove('hidden');
        const perChild = Math.round(basePrice * (selectedCountry.multiplier || 1));
        const total = perChild * selectedQty;
        const dailyPerChild = (perChild / 30).toFixed(2);
        if (mobileTotalPrice) mobileTotalPrice.textContent = isMonthly ? `$${total}/mo` : `$${(total * 12).toLocaleString()}/yr`;
        if (mobilePriceDetail) mobilePriceDetail.textContent = `${selectedQty} ${selectedQty === 1 ? 'child' : 'children'} × $${perChild}/mo`;
        if (mobileDailyPrice) mobileDailyPrice.textContent = `That's just $${dailyPerChild}/day per child`;
      } else if (mobilePriceSummary) {
        mobilePriceSummary.classList.add('hidden');
      }

      updateButtonState();
    };

    // Country selection
    countryBtns.forEach(btn => {
      btn.addEventListener('click', () => {
        // Reset all country buttons (both mobile and desktop)
        countryBtns.forEach(b => {
          // Desktop styles reset
          b.classList.remove('border-[#d97706]', 'bg-[#d97706]/5', 'shadow-[inset_0_0_0_3px_rgba(217,119,6,0.2)]');
          b.classList.add('border-gray-200');
          // Mobile styles reset (only apply to mobile buttons that have a radio indicator)
          const radio = b.querySelector('.country-radio');
          if (radio) {
            b.classList.remove('border-l-[#d97706]');
            b.classList.add('border-l-transparent');
            radio.innerHTML = '';
            radio.classList.remove('border-[#d97706]');
            radio.classList.add('border-gray-300');
          }
        });

        // Highlight selected — desktop styles
        btn.classList.remove('border-gray-200');
        btn.classList.add('border-[#d97706]', 'bg-[#d97706]/5', 'shadow-[inset_0_0_0_3px_rgba(217,119,6,0.2)]');
        // Highlight selected — mobile styles (only if this is a mobile button)
        const radio = btn.querySelector('.country-radio');
        if (radio) {
          btn.classList.remove('border-l-transparent');
          btn.classList.add('border-l-[#d97706]');
          radio.innerHTML = '<div class="w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-[#d97706]"></div>';
          radio.classList.remove('border-gray-300');
          radio.classList.add('border-[#d97706]');
        }

        selectedCountry = {
          id: btn.dataset.country || 'pakistan',
          name: btn.dataset.name || 'Pakistan',
          flag: btn.dataset.flag || '🇵🇰',
          multiplier: parseFloat(btn.dataset.multiplier || '1')
        };
        updateUI();

        // On mobile scroll fully to quantity section, on desktop nudge down slightly
        const isMobile = window.innerWidth < 1024;
        if (isMobile) {
          setTimeout(() => scrollToSection(quantitySection, true), 300);
        } else {
          // Nudge scroll down ~150px so step 2 peeks into view, but step 1 stays visible
          setTimeout(() => {
            window.scrollBy({ top: 100, behavior: 'smooth' });
            if (quantitySection) {
              quantitySection.classList.add('outline', 'outline-2', 'outline-[#d97706]/60');
              setTimeout(() => {
                quantitySection.classList.remove('outline', 'outline-2', 'outline-[#d97706]/60');
              }, 1500);
            }
          }, 300);
        }
      });
    });

    // Pulse the sponsor button to draw attention
    const pulseButton = () => {
      if (sponsorBtn) {
        sponsorBtn.classList.add('animate-pulse-glow');
        setTimeout(() => sponsorBtn.classList.remove('animate-pulse-glow'), 2000);
      }
      if (mobileSponsorBtn) {
        mobileSponsorBtn.classList.add('animate-pulse-glow');
        setTimeout(() => mobileSponsorBtn.classList.remove('animate-pulse-glow'), 2000);
      }
    };

    // Quantity tile selection
    qtyTiles.forEach(tile => {
      tile.addEventListener('click', () => {
        isCustom = false;
        if (customToggle) customToggle.checked = false;
        if (customQtyInput) customQtyInput.classList.add('hidden');

        qtyTiles.forEach(t => {
          const isMobileCircle = t.classList.contains('rounded-full');
          // Reset desktop styles
          t.classList.remove('border-[#d97706]', 'bg-[#d97706]/5', 'bg-[#d97706]', 'shadow-[inset_0_0_0_3px_rgba(217,119,6,0.2)]', 'scale-105');
          t.classList.add('border-gray-200');
          if (isMobileCircle) {
            t.classList.add('bg-white');
          }
          // Reset mobile text colors
          const num = t.querySelector('.qty-number');
          const lbl = t.querySelector('.qty-label');
          if (num) { num.classList.remove('text-white'); num.classList.add('text-gray-700'); }
          if (lbl) { lbl.classList.remove('text-white/90'); lbl.classList.add('text-gray-400'); }
        });

        const isMobileCircle = tile.classList.contains('rounded-full');
        tile.classList.remove('border-gray-200');

        if (isMobileCircle) {
          // Mobile: filled orange circle with white text
          tile.classList.remove('bg-white');
          tile.classList.add('border-[#d97706]', 'bg-[#d97706]');
          const num = tile.querySelector('.qty-number');
          const lbl = tile.querySelector('.qty-label');
          if (num) { num.classList.remove('text-gray-700'); num.classList.add('text-white'); }
          if (lbl) { lbl.classList.remove('text-gray-400'); lbl.classList.add('text-white/90'); }
        } else {
          // Desktop: bordered highlight with scale
          tile.classList.add('border-[#d97706]', 'bg-[#d97706]/5', 'shadow-[inset_0_0_0_3px_rgba(217,119,6,0.2)]', 'scale-105');
        }

        selectedQty = parseInt(tile.dataset.qty || '2');
        updateUI();

        if (isSelectionComplete()) {
          // Both selections made - scroll to sponsor button and pulse it
          setTimeout(() => {
            scrollToSection(sponsorBtn?.closest('.bg-white.rounded-2xl') || sponsorBtn, false);
            pulseButton();
          }, 300);
        } else if (!selectedCountry) {
          // Children selected but no country yet - nudge user to pick a country
          setTimeout(() => {
            scrollToSection(regionSection, true);
            // Flash the Step 1 header to draw attention
            const step1Header = regionSection?.querySelector('h2, h3, .step-header');
            if (step1Header) {
              step1Header.classList.add('text-[#d97706]');
              setTimeout(() => step1Header.classList.remove('text-[#d97706]'), 2000);
            }
            // Show a brief toast-style message
            showSelectCountryToast();
          }, 300);
        }
      });
    });

    // Sync both mobile and desktop custom qty fields
    const syncCustomQtyFields = (newVal) => {
      const val = newVal.toString();
      if (customQty) customQty.value = val;
      if (mobileCustomQty) mobileCustomQty.value = val;
    };

    // Custom toggle
    customToggle?.addEventListener('change', () => {
      isCustom = customToggle.checked;
      if (customQtyInput) {
        customQtyInput.classList.toggle('hidden', !isCustom);
      }
      if (isCustom) {
        qtyTiles.forEach(t => {
          const isMobileCircle = t.classList.contains('rounded-full');
          t.classList.remove('border-[#d97706]', 'bg-[#d97706]/5', 'bg-[#d97706]', 'shadow-[inset_0_0_0_3px_rgba(217,119,6,0.2)]', 'scale-105');
          t.classList.add('border-gray-200');
          if (isMobileCircle) t.classList.add('bg-white');
          const num = t.querySelector('.qty-number');
          const lbl = t.querySelector('.qty-label');
          if (num) { num.classList.remove('text-white'); num.classList.add('text-gray-700'); }
          if (lbl) { lbl.classList.remove('text-white/90'); lbl.classList.add('text-gray-400'); }
        });
        selectedQty = parseInt(customQty?.value || mobileCustomQty?.value || '4');
        syncCustomQtyFields(selectedQty);
        updateUI();
        // Nudge to country selection if not yet chosen
        if (!selectedCountry) {
          setTimeout(() => {
            scrollToSection(regionSection, true);
            showSelectCountryToast();
          }, 300);
        }
      }
    });

    // Shared decrease/increase logic
    const handleCustomDecrease = () => {
      const current = parseInt(customQty?.value || mobileCustomQty?.value || '4');
      if (current > 1) {
        const newVal = current - 1;
        syncCustomQtyFields(newVal);
        selectedQty = newVal;
        updateUI();
      }
    };

    const handleCustomIncrease = () => {
      const current = parseInt(customQty?.value || mobileCustomQty?.value || '4');
      if (current < 100) {
        const newVal = current + 1;
        syncCustomQtyFields(newVal);
        selectedQty = newVal;
        updateUI();
      }
    };

    const handleCustomInput = (inputEl) => {
      selectedQty = parseInt(inputEl.value) || 1;
      syncCustomQtyFields(selectedQty);
      updateUI();
    };

    // Desktop custom quantity controls
    customDecrease?.addEventListener('click', handleCustomDecrease);
    customIncrease?.addEventListener('click', handleCustomIncrease);
    customQty?.addEventListener('input', () => handleCustomInput(customQty));

    // Mobile custom quantity controls
    mobileCustomDecrease?.addEventListener('click', handleCustomDecrease);
    mobileCustomIncrease?.addEventListener('click', handleCustomIncrease);
    mobileCustomQty?.addEventListener('input', () => handleCustomInput(mobileCustomQty));

    // Frequency toggle
    freqMonthly?.addEventListener('click', () => {
      isMonthly = true;
      freqMonthly.classList.add('bg-white', 'text-[#d97706]', 'shadow-sm');
      freqMonthly.classList.remove('text-gray-500');
      freqYearly?.classList.remove('bg-white', 'text-[#d97706]', 'shadow-sm');
      freqYearly?.classList.add('text-gray-500');
      updateUI();
    });

    freqYearly?.addEventListener('click', () => {
      isMonthly = false;
      freqYearly.classList.add('bg-white', 'text-[#d97706]', 'shadow-sm');
      freqYearly.classList.remove('text-gray-500');
      freqMonthly?.classList.remove('bg-white', 'text-[#d97706]', 'shadow-sm');
      freqMonthly?.classList.add('text-gray-500');
      updateUI();
    });

    // Sponsor button - Add to cart
    const handleSponsor = (e) => {
      // Check if selection is complete
      if (!isSelectionComplete() || !selectedCountry) {
        return;
      }

      const btn = e.currentTarget;
      const monthlyTotal = selectedQty * basePrice * selectedCountry.multiplier;
      const amount = isMonthly ? monthlyTotal : monthlyTotal * 12;
      const frequency = isMonthly ? 'monthly' : 'yearly';
      const childText = selectedQty === 1 ? 'Child' : 'Children';

      // Use the global addToCart function
      if (typeof window.addToCart === 'function') {
        const childLabel = selectedQty === 1 ? '1 Child' : selectedQty + ' Children';
        window.addToCart({
          id: `orphan-sponsorship-${selectedCountry.id}-${frequency}`,
          type: frequency,
          recurringInterval: frequency,
          name: `Orphan Sponsorship - ${selectedCountry.name} (${childLabel})`,
          amount: amount,
          quantity: 1,
          campaign: 'Orphan Sponsorship',
          campaignSlug: 'sponsor-an-orphan',
          image: '/images/qurbani-foundation-orphan-sponsorship.webp'
        });
        // Open the cart
        if (window.donationCart?.openCart) {
          window.donationCart.openCart();
        }
      }

      // Show success feedback on button
      const btnTextEl = btn.querySelector('span');
      const originalText = btnTextEl?.textContent || '';
      if (btnTextEl) {
        btnTextEl.textContent = 'Added to Cart!';
      }
      btn.classList.remove('bg-[#d97706]');
      btn.classList.add('bg-[#15803d]');

      setTimeout(() => {
        if (btnTextEl) btnTextEl.textContent = originalText;
        btn.classList.remove('bg-[#15803d]');
        btn.classList.add('bg-[#d97706]');
      }, 2000);
    };

    // Desktop button - smart behavior based on selection state
    sponsorBtn?.addEventListener('click', (e) => {
      if (isSelectionComplete()) {
        // Selection complete - add to cart
        handleSponsor(e);
      } else {
        // Guide user to the section they need to complete
        if (!selectedCountry) {
          scrollToSection(regionSection, true);
        } else if (selectedQty === 0) {
          scrollToSection(quantitySection, true);
        }
      }
    });

    // Mobile button - smart behavior based on selection state
    mobileSponsorBtn?.addEventListener('click', (e) => {
      if (isSelectionComplete()) {
        // Selection complete - add to cart
        handleSponsor(e);
      } else {
        // Guide user to the section they need to complete
        if (!selectedCountry) {
          // Need to select region first
          scrollToSection(regionSection, true);
        } else if (selectedQty === 0) {
          // Need to select quantity
          scrollToSection(quantitySection, true);
        }
      }
    });

    // Live counter removed

    // ============ RECENT SPONSORS ============
    const recentSponsorsContainer = document.getElementById('recent-sponsors');
    const STORAGE_KEY = 'orphan_sponsors_data';
    const MAX_SPONSOR_AGE = 10 * 60 * 60 * 1000; // 10 hours max age

    // Pool of names
    const namePool = [
      { name: 'Ahmed R.', location: 'California' },
      { name: 'Fatima K.', location: 'New York' },
      { name: 'Omar S.', location: 'Texas' },
      { name: 'Aisha M.', location: 'Illinois' },
      { name: 'Ibrahim H.', location: 'Florida' },
      { name: 'Yasmin A.', location: 'New Jersey' },
      { name: 'Khalid M.', location: 'Michigan' },
      { name: 'Mariam S.', location: 'Georgia' },
      { name: 'Hassan B.', location: 'Virginia' },
      { name: 'Nadia Z.', location: 'Pennsylvania' },
      { name: 'Yusuf T.', location: 'Ohio' },
      { name: 'Layla H.', location: 'North Carolina' },
      { name: 'Bilal K.', location: 'Arizona' },
      { name: 'Samira J.', location: 'Colorado' },
      { name: 'Tariq N.', location: 'Washington' },
      { name: 'Zainab Q.', location: 'Maryland' },
    ];

    // Get stored data or initialize
    const getStoredData = () => {
      try {
        const stored = localStorage.getItem(STORAGE_KEY);
        if (stored) {
          return JSON.parse(stored);
        }
      } catch (e) {}

      // Initialize with default sponsors
      const now = Date.now();
      return {
        sponsors: [
          { name: 'Ahmed R.', location: 'California', qty: 2, timestamp: now - 1 * 60 * 60 * 1000 },
          { name: 'Fatima K.', location: 'New York', qty: 3, timestamp: now - 3 * 60 * 60 * 1000 },
          { name: 'Omar S.', location: 'Texas', qty: 1, timestamp: now - 5 * 60 * 60 * 1000 },
          { name: 'Aisha M.', location: 'Illinois', qty: 2, timestamp: now - 7 * 60 * 60 * 1000 },
          { name: 'Ibrahim H.', location: 'Florida', qty: 5, timestamp: now - 9 * 60 * 60 * 1000 },
        ],
        scheduledFakes: [],
        lastRealDonation: 0
      };
    };

    // Save to localStorage
    const saveData = (data) => {
      try {
        localStorage.setItem(STORAGE_KEY, JSON.stringify(data));
      } catch (e) {}
    };

    // Get a random name not in current list
    const getNewSponsor = (currentNames) => {
      const available = namePool.filter(n => !currentNames.includes(n.name));
      const pick = available.length > 0
        ? available[Math.floor(Math.random() * available.length)]
        : namePool[Math.floor(Math.random() * namePool.length)];

      return {
        ...pick,
        qty: [1, 2, 2, 2, 3, 3, 5][Math.floor(Math.random() * 7)],
        timestamp: Date.now()
      };
    };

    // Sort sponsors by timestamp (newest first)
    const sortSponsors = (sponsors) => {
      return sponsors.sort((a, b) => b.timestamp - a.timestamp);
    };

    // Load data
    let storedData = getStoredData();
    let displayedSponsors = storedData.sponsors;
    let scheduledFakes = storedData.scheduledFakes;
    let lastRealDonation = storedData.lastRealDonation;
    const now = Date.now();

    // Process any scheduled fake sponsors that are due
    const dueSchedules = scheduledFakes.filter(t => t <= now);
    const remainingSchedules = scheduledFakes.filter(t => t > now);

    if (dueSchedules.length > 0) {
      // Add fake sponsors for each due schedule
      for (const scheduleTime of dueSchedules) {
        const currentNames = displayedSponsors.map(s => s.name);
        const newSponsor = getNewSponsor(currentNames);
        // Set timestamp to when it was scheduled (with small random offset)
        newSponsor.timestamp = scheduleTime + Math.floor(Math.random() * 10) * 60 * 1000;
        displayedSponsors.push(newSponsor);
      }

      scheduledFakes = remainingSchedules;
    }

    // Sort and remove old sponsors
    displayedSponsors = sortSponsors(displayedSponsors);

    // Remove sponsors older than MAX_SPONSOR_AGE
    displayedSponsors = displayedSponsors.filter(s => (now - s.timestamp) < MAX_SPONSOR_AGE);

    // Keep only top 5
    displayedSponsors = displayedSponsors.slice(0, 5);

    // If less than 5, fill with spread-out fake sponsors
    while (displayedSponsors.length < 5) {
      const currentNames = displayedSponsors.map(s => s.name);
      const newSponsor = getNewSponsor(currentNames);
      const existingCount = displayedSponsors.length;
      newSponsor.timestamp = now - (1 + existingCount * 2) * 60 * 60 * 1000;
      displayedSponsors.push(newSponsor);
    }

    displayedSponsors = sortSponsors(displayedSponsors);
    saveData({ sponsors: displayedSponsors, scheduledFakes, lastRealDonation });

    // Format time ago
    const formatTimeAgo = (timestamp) => {
      const seconds = Math.floor((Date.now() - timestamp) / 1000);
      if (seconds < 60) return 'Just now';
      const minutes = Math.floor(seconds / 60);
      if (minutes === 1) return '1 min ago';
      if (minutes < 60) return `${minutes} min ago`;
      const hours = Math.floor(minutes / 60);
      if (hours === 1) return '1 hour ago';
      return `${hours} hours ago`;
    };

    // Render sponsors list
    const renderSponsors = () => {
      if (!recentSponsorsContainer) return;

      const toShow = displayedSponsors.slice(0, 5);

      recentSponsorsContainer.innerHTML = toShow.map(sponsor => `
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between py-2 border-b border-gray-100 last:border-0 ${sponsor.isReal ? 'bg-amber-50 -mx-2 px-2 rounded-lg' : ''}">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#d97706] to-[#b45309] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold">
              ${sponsor.name.charAt(0)}
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="font-medium text-gray-800">${sponsor.name}</div>
              <div class="text-xs text-gray-500">${sponsor.location}</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="text-right">
            <div class="font-medium text-gray-800">${sponsor.qty} ${sponsor.qty === 1 ? 'child' : 'children'}</div>
            <div class="text-xs text-gray-400">${formatTimeAgo(sponsor.timestamp)}</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      `).join('');
    };

    // Schedule fake sponsors after a real donation
    const scheduleFakeSponsors = () => {
      const now = Date.now();

      // Schedule fake donations: ~1 hour later, ~3 hours later, ~6 hours later
      // Add randomness: ±15 minutes
      const randomMinutes = () => (Math.random() - 0.5) * 30 * 60 * 1000; // ±15 min

      scheduledFakes = [
        now + 1 * 60 * 60 * 1000 + randomMinutes(),  // ~1 hour
        now + 3 * 60 * 60 * 1000 + randomMinutes(),  // ~3 hours
        now + 6 * 60 * 60 * 1000 + randomMinutes(),  // ~6 hours
      ];

      lastRealDonation = now;
      saveData({ sponsors: displayedSponsors, scheduledFakes, lastRealDonation });
    };

    // Add real sponsor when someone donates
    const addRealSponsor = (name, location, qty) => {
      // Add new real sponsor
      displayedSponsors.unshift({
        name,
        location,
        qty,
        timestamp: Date.now(),
        isReal: true
      });

      // Sort by timestamp
      displayedSponsors = sortSponsors(displayedSponsors);

      // Remove oldest FAKE sponsors first to keep at 5
      while (displayedSponsors.length > 5) {
        let oldestFakeIndex = -1;

        for (let i = displayedSponsors.length - 1; i >= 0; i--) {
          if (!displayedSponsors[i].isReal) {
            oldestFakeIndex = i;
            break;
          }
        }

        if (oldestFakeIndex !== -1) {
          displayedSponsors.splice(oldestFakeIndex, 1);
        } else {
          // All real - remove oldest
          displayedSponsors.pop();
        }
      }

      // Schedule fake sponsors to appear after this real donation
      scheduleFakeSponsors();

      renderSponsors();
    };

    // Expose for external use
    window.addRealSponsor = addRealSponsor;

    // Initialize
    renderSponsors();

    // Update times every minute
    setInterval(() => {
      renderSponsors();
    }, 60000);

    // Check for scheduled fakes every 5 minutes
    setInterval(() => {
      const now = Date.now();
      const dueNow = scheduledFakes.filter(t => t <= now);

      if (dueNow.length > 0) {
        // Add the due fake sponsors
        for (const t of dueNow) {
          const currentNames = displayedSponsors.map(s => s.name);
          const newSponsor = getNewSponsor(currentNames);
          newSponsor.timestamp = t;
          displayedSponsors.push(newSponsor);
        }

        // Remove processed schedules
        scheduledFakes = scheduledFakes.filter(t => t > now);

        // Sort and trim to 5
        displayedSponsors = sortSponsors(displayedSponsors);

        // Remove oldest fake if more than 5
        while (displayedSponsors.length > 5) {
          let oldestFakeIndex = -1;
          for (let i = displayedSponsors.length - 1; i >= 0; i--) {
            if (!displayedSponsors[i].isReal) {
              oldestFakeIndex = i;
              break;
            }
          }
          if (oldestFakeIndex !== -1) {
            displayedSponsors.splice(oldestFakeIndex, 1);
          } else {
            displayedSponsors.pop();
          }
        }

        saveData({ sponsors: displayedSponsors, scheduledFakes, lastRealDonation });
        renderSponsors();
      }
    }, 5 * 60 * 1000);

    // Click handler for summary label
    summaryQtyLabel?.addEventListener('click', () => {
      if (!selectedCountry) {
        scrollToSection(regionSection, true);
      } else if (selectedQty === 0) {
        scrollToSection(quantitySection, true);
      }
    });

    // Click handler for summary country
    summaryCountry?.addEventListener('click', () => {
      if (!selectedCountry) {
        scrollToSection(regionSection, true);
      }
    });

    // Initial visual stack link listener
    attachVisualStackListener();

    // Pre-select Greatest Need by default (without scrolling)
    const generalBtn = document.querySelector('[data-country="general"]');
    if (generalBtn) {
      // Highlight the button
      generalBtn.classList.remove('border-gray-200');
      generalBtn.classList.add('border-[#d97706]', 'bg-[#d97706]/5', 'shadow-[inset_0_0_0_3px_rgba(217,119,6,0.2)]');
      const radio = generalBtn.querySelector('.country-radio');
      if (radio) {
        generalBtn.classList.remove('border-l-transparent');
        generalBtn.classList.add('border-l-[#d97706]');
        radio.innerHTML = '<div class="w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-[#d97706]"></div>';
        radio.classList.remove('border-gray-300');
        radio.classList.add('border-[#d97706]');
      }
      // Set state
      selectedCountry = {
        id: generalBtn.dataset.country || 'general',
        name: generalBtn.dataset.name || 'Greatest Need',
        flag: generalBtn.dataset.flag || '🌍',
        multiplier: parseFloat(generalBtn.dataset.multiplier || '1')
      };
    }

    // Card button handlers
    // 1. Sponsor in Palestine → add $100/month to cart
    const btnPalestine = document.getElementById('btn-sponsor-palestine');
    if (btnPalestine) {
      btnPalestine.addEventListener('click', () => {
        if (typeof window.addToCart === 'function') {
          window.addToCart({
            id: 'orphan-sponsorship-palestine-monthly',
            type: 'monthly',
            recurringInterval: 'monthly',
            name: 'Orphan Sponsorship - Palestine (1 Child)',
            amount: 100,
            quantity: 1,
            campaign: 'Orphan Sponsorship',
            campaignSlug: 'sponsor-an-orphan',
            image: '/images/qurbani-foundation-orphan-sponsorship5.webp'
          });
          if (window.donationCart?.openCart) window.donationCart.openCart();
        }
      });
    }

    // 2. Become a Monthly Donor → scroll to donation box
    const btnMonthly = document.getElementById('btn-monthly-donor');
    if (btnMonthly) {
      btnMonthly.addEventListener('click', () => {
        const donateBox = document.getElementById('region-section') || document.querySelector('[data-donate]');
        if (donateBox) {
          const offset = 100;
          const pos = donateBox.getBoundingClientRect().top + window.pageYOffset;
          window.scrollTo({ top: pos - offset, behavior: 'smooth' });
          donateBox.classList.add('outline', 'outline-2', 'outline-[#d97706]/60');
          setTimeout(() => donateBox.classList.remove('outline', 'outline-2', 'outline-[#d97706]/60'), 2000);
        }
      });
    }

    // 3. Shared Sponsorship → add $25/month Greatest Need to cart
    const btnShared = document.getElementById('btn-shared-sponsorship');
    if (btnShared) {
      btnShared.addEventListener('click', () => {
        if (typeof window.addToCart === 'function') {
          window.addToCart({
            id: 'orphan-sponsorship-shared-monthly',
            type: 'monthly',
            recurringInterval: 'monthly',
            name: 'Shared Orphan Sponsorship - Greatest Need (1 Child)',
            amount: 25,
            quantity: 1,
            campaign: 'Orphan Sponsorship',
            campaignSlug: 'sponsor-an-orphan',
            image: '/images/qurbani-foundation-orphan-sponsorship1.webp'
          });
          if (window.donationCart?.openCart) window.donationCart.openCart();
        }
      });
    }

    // Initialize
    updateUI();
  });
</script>

